      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "NESPELIM. Wash, via Wilbur,\nWash, Sept. 27.--Far out across the\nbig Nespelim. on the hilltops which\noverlook this deserted. silent camp\nof the Nez Perces, lone kluchman\ntakes up a weary vigil just before\nthe break OF day.\n\n\n1t Is Wa-win-te- pe-koet. the aged\nfirst wife OF Chief Joseph, who, each\nmorning since the death of the great\ntyee. goes to lament and to pray to\nthe Soc-a-lee-tyee, Great Almighty"
    }
  ]
